# This directory holds the PLOS One CCL-2023 cold chain dataset.
#
# Download instructions:
#   1. Open https://journals.plos.org/plosone/article?id=10.1371/journal.pone.0315322
#   2. Scroll to "Supporting Information"
#   3. Download S1.csv, S2.csv, S3.csv
#   4. Place them here: eval/datasets/plosone/
#
# Then run:
#   python eval/preprocess_plosone.py
#   python eval/baseline_eval.py
#   STATE_ENGINE_URL=http://localhost:8000 python eval/dataset_eval.py
#
# License: CC BY — cite the paper in your references.
# This .gitkeep file is intentional — the CSVs are NOT committed to git.
